The '''Alderaan Alliance''' was the political organization of [[Alderaanian/Legends|Alderaanians]] who had survived the [[Destruction of Alderaan/Legends|Destruction of Alderaan]]. It compiled a list of all individuals affiliated with the [[Death Star/Legends|Death Star]] project, and publicized it, hoping they would come to stand trial.

